metadata.name: Do It Butthurt Chicago
metadata.description:
I was the number wun holdr in Gutter Cat Gang.  
But some things got deelayed and my gang bags went down.  
Now I whine on Twitter all day like a little bitch and can't stop thinking about Gang.  
I'm obsessed and need hlep frankly, my obsession with Ric in particular is suss AF. BTW I only hav clones but I am still the number wun holdr. Just in kase u dunt know.
